    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 7,
      "marker": "○",
      "text": "透過異常值檢測（如基於MAD 的方法）篩選感測器錯誤數據。",
      "pageIndex": 95,
      "bbox": [
        136.12,
        425.65,
        503.64,
        439.1
      ],
      "id": "block-70",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c7",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "網路安全與異常行為偵測",
      "pageIndex": 95,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        450.75,
        260.71,
        464.2
      ],
      "id": "block-71",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c7",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "網路安全分析需即時監控流量與用戶行為，統計推論是異常偵測的基礎、而大數據中的串流資料和高維度特性將增加計算挑戰。",
      "pageIndex": 95,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        475.71,
        518.19,
        514.12
      ],
      "id": "block-72",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c7",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "應用方式：",
      "pageIndex": 95,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        525.75,
        202.15,
        539.2
      ],
      "id": "block-73",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c7",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 7,
      "marker": "○",
      "text": "建立行為分佈模型（如常態分佈），檢測異常登入頻率或地理位置（例如使用Z 分數識別異常值）。",
      "pageIndex": 95,
      "bbox": [
        136.12,
        550.71,
        518.3,
        589.12
      ],
      "id": "block-74",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c7",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 7,
      "marker": "○",
      "text": "利用密度估計法（如核密度估計）分析流量模式，識別DDoS 攻擊等異常行為。",
      "pageIndex": 95,
      "bbox": [
        136.12,
        600.75,
        518.4,
        639.19
      ],
      "id": "block-75",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c7",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 7,
      "marker": "○",
      "text": "運用滑動視窗統計（如移動平均）設計即時警示系統，監控異常趨勢。",
      "pageIndex": 95,
      "bbox": [
        136.12,
        650.7,
        518.2,
        689.23
      ],
      "id": "block-76",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c7",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "社會科學與政策分析",
      "pageIndex": 95,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        700.74,
        235.51,
        714.19
      ],
      "id": "block-77",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c7",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "社會調查和人口普查數據為政策評估提供基礎，而結構性偏誤（如抽樣偏差）可能影響推論泛化性。",
      "pageIndex": 95,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        725.7,
        518.2,
        764.22
      ],
      "id": "block-78",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c7",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "應用方式：",
      "pageIndex": 96,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        100.66,
        202.15,
        114.11
      ],
      "id": "block-79",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c7",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 7,
      "marker": "○",
      "text": "使用多變量迴歸分析社經變數（如收入、教育）與行為（如投票率） 的關係。",
      "pageIndex": 96,
      "bbox": [
        136.12,
        125.62,
        524.47,
        164.15
      ],
      "id": "block-80",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c7",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 7,
      "marker": "○",
      "text": "透過抽樣加權與置信區間推估全國性結論，校正非隨機抽樣偏誤。",
      "pageIndex": 96,
      "bbox": [
        136.12,
        175.66,
        518.88,
        189.11
      ],
      "id": "block-81",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c7",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "智慧城市與物聯網資料應用",
      "pageIndex": 96,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        200.62,
        273.31,
        214.07
      ],
      "id": "block-82",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c7",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "物聯網（IoT）和城市感測器產生高頻率、即時數據，統計學幫助優化城市資源分配、而資料的時空複雜性增加分析難度。",
      "pageIndex": 96,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        225.7,
        518.1,
        264.14
      ],
      "id": "block-83",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c7",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "應用方式：",
      "pageIndex": 96,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        275.65,
        202.15,
        289.1
      ],
      "id": "block-84",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c7",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 7,
      "marker": "○",
      "text": "使用近似分位數（如t-digest）處理高頻數據，快速估計交通流量分佈。",
      "pageIndex": 96,
      "bbox": [
        136.12,
        300.73,
        518.15,
        339.14
      ],
      "id": "block-85",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c7",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 7,
      "marker": "○",
      "text": "透過時空統計模型（如空間自迴歸）分析交通或能耗模式，預測擁堵熱點。",
      "pageIndex": 96,
      "bbox": [
        136.12,
        350.65,
        518.22,
        389.18
      ],
      "id": "block-86",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c7",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 7,
      "marker": "○",
      "text": "運用區間估計與趨勢檢測調整交通號誌或能源分配。",
      "pageIndex": 96,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        400.69,
        443.25,
        773.34
      ],
      "id": "block-87",
      "nodeId": "mid-s2c7",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    }
